<section class="section" style="background-color: var(--color-neutral);">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Design Implementation</h2>
    <p class="mb-lg">
      Every aspect of this website demonstrates Flat Design principles:
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="principle-card" style="background-color: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="principle-number" style="color: var(--color-white);">Flat</div>
        <h3 class="principle-title" style="color: var(--color-white);">No Depth Effects</h3>
        <p class="principle-description" style="color: var(--color-white);">
          Zero shadows, gradients, or 3D effects. Pure two-dimensional design throughout 
          the entire site. Buttons, cards, and UI elements are completely flat.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="principle-card" style="background-color: var(--color-success); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="principle-number" style="color: var(--color-white);">Colors</div>
        <h3 class="principle-title" style="color: var(--color-white);">Flat UI Palette</h3>
        <p class="principle-description" style="color: var(--color-white);">
          Bright, vibrant Flat UI Colors palette: #3498DB (blue), #2ECC71 (green), 
          #F39C12 (orange), #E74C3C (red). Bold color blocks create visual interest.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="principle-card" style="background-color: var(--color-warning); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="principle-number" style="color: var(--color-white);">Type</div>
        <h3 class="principle-title" style="color: var(--color-white);">Open Sans</h3>
        <p class="principle-description" style="color: var(--color-white);">
          Clean sans-serif typography with bold weights (600-800). Clear hierarchy 
          through size and weight. Modern, readable, perfectly flat.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="principle-card" style="background-color: var(--color-danger); color: var(--color-white);">
        <div class="principle-number" style="color: var(--color-white);">Simple</div>
        <h3 class="principle-title" style="color: var(--color-white);">Minimal UI</h3>
        <p class="principle-description" style="color: var(--color-white);">
          Simple rectangular cards with 4px border-radius. Clean layouts. Essential 
          elements only. Content-focused design.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

